channel.title: Can't connect to rsca server using RSCA v3 Client
channel.description: I downloaded rsca v3 client off rapidshare from original rscangel server, and it won't connect to my current server. I changed the ip in settings.ini to the server's ip. The client that comes with the source works. Is there a newer version of the rsca distributable client? If so can somoene upload?
